{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Launch a public inquiry into how taxpayers fund the monarchy",
        "additional_details": "I want the Government to also look into publishing a full financial report at the end of every tax year which shows taxpayer spending on the monarchy.",
        "background": "I want the Government to launch a public inquiry into how taxpayers fund the monarchy and whether current funding is fit for purpose. I also want full transparency and for the inquiry to investigate how taxpayer money is used every financial year in relation to the monarchy.",
